next Story: Some story about person_signup

  As a Person
  I want to be able to signup
  So that I can participate on the site
  
  Scenario: Invalid signup data is submitted
    When I signup with invalid data
    Then 0 new users should be created
    And 0 new people should be created
    
  Scenario: Invalid signup data is submitted requesting HTML
    When I signup with invalid data
    Then the person signup form should be rendered
    And the response should contain an error notice
    
  Scenario: Invalid signup data is submitted requesting XML
    When I request an XML response
    And I signup with invalid data
    Then the XML response should contain an error notice
  
  Scenario: Invalid signup data is submitted requesting JSON
    When I request a JSON response
    And I signup with invalid data
    Then the JSON response should contain an error notice
   
  Scenario: Valid signup data is submitted
    When I signup with valid data
    Then 1 new user should be created
    And 1 new person should be created
    
  Scenario: Valid signup data is submitted requesting HTML
    When I signup with valid data
    Then the response should contain an activation notice
    
  Scenario: Valid signup data is submitted requesting XML
    When I request an XML response
    And I signup with valid data
    Then the XML response should contain an activation notice
    
  Scenario: Valid signup data is submitted requesting JSON
    When I request a JSON response
    And I signup with valid data
    Then the JSON response should contain an activation notice
    